reviewText: These video clips are moderately instructive and well done, if fairly dated (most appear to be from the 1980's and 90's).  My low rating mainly reflects my opinion that this set is greatly overpriced.  If I could do it again, I wouldn't pay over $15-20.  You will be disappointed if you pay more, trust me.
Hollywood, has to get its share of the money, irregardless of right or wrong! Poor Dr. Covey trying to do good work in the world, only to be screwed by Hollywood again!
